725880f-a.title: Queens: 147th Avenue - Brookville Boulevard
725880f-a.text:
147th Avenue (telephone poles), south side, east from
Brookville Boulevard, showing a view across farmland which
was owned by one George Mount in 1909. The inscription on
the shack reads: Laurelton Plnza-- Local Cffice-- Lots for
Sale.
'. L Sperr  March 9, 1927
